[$mdisplay] R_1 +R_2 \amp \rightarrow R_2\\
[$n] R_1 +R_3 \amp \rightarrow R_3\\
[$p] R_2 +R_3 \amp \rightarrow R_3
\end{aligned}
```]

[_]*{$answer}{5}

